content: No rooms match this filter. Try a different one or clear filter to view all rooms.

comment.text: "No rooms match this filter. This message is displayed when a user searches for rooms that don't meet their criteria and is typically shown on an empty screen after clearing filters or changing search parameters."

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'təmiz filtri sınayın' is grammatically awkward. 'Təmizləyin' (clear) would be more natural.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Bütün otaqlara baxmaq üçün fərqli filtri və ya filtri təmizləyin.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Armenian translation uses a colon (:) after the first sentence, which creates an unnatural pause.  In this context, a conjunction or a comma might be more appropriate.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider replacing the colon with a comma or a conjunction like 'և' (and).

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ' is misspelled. It should be 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'clear filter' is not ideal. 'Limpar os filtros' is technically correct but sounds a bit clunky. A more natural phrasing would be 'remover os filtros'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nenhum quarto corresponde a este filtro. Tente um filtro diferente ou remova os filtros para ver todas as salas.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "Filtru de sală nu a produs rezultate" is a literal and slightly awkward translation of 'No rooms match this filter.' A more natural Romanian phrasing would convey the meaning better.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nici o sală nu corespunde filtrului ales. Încercați un alt filtru sau ștergeți filtrul pentru a vedea toate sălile.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'sală' appears multiple times. While technically correct, in this context 'cameră' might be more appropriate.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider replacing 'sală' with 'cameră' for greater naturalness, especially if the rooms being referred to are smaller or private.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'පෙරහන' is repeated unnecessarily. While technically correct, it's a bit clunky.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: මෙම පෙරහන් වලට ගැළපෙන කාමර නැත. වෙනත් පෙරහන් යොදා ගන්න හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට හිස් කරන්න.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට හිස් කරන්න' is a bit awkward. A more natural phrasing would improve readability.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට පෙරහන් ඉවත් කරන්න.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'филтер' is often written as 'филтер'.
While grammatically correct, the phrasing 'Пробајте други или обришите филтер' is slightly less natural.  A more common phrasing would be 'Изаберите други филтер или обришите га'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Изаберите други филтер или обришите га

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Serbian translation 'Nijedna soba se ne poklapa sa ovim filterom' is a literal translation and sounds slightly unnatural. A more idiomatic phrasing would be preferred.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nijedna soba ne odgovara ovom filteru.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'obrišite filter da biste pregledali sve sobe' is grammatically correct but a bit verbose. It can be shortened for better flow.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: obrišite filter da vidite sve sobe.
